Standard and Poor's Corp said itaffirmed the BB-plus rating on AFG Industries Inc's 185 mlndlrs of subordinated debt.    S and P said it believed AFG would make acquisitions ofmoderate size in the next few years. AFG's healthy cash flowand pro forma cash balances of 169 mln dlrs at September 30,1986, should be adequate to fund internal expansion andmoderate acquisitions.    While AFG's participation in a 1.4 billion dlr bid for LearSiegler Inc was aggressive, AFG was mainly interested in Lear'sprofitable auto glass operations, S and P noted. Reuter&#3;